data.description: One of the largest floor plans in Oceana!  Detached 1498 sq. ft. atrium style elevated home with lots of privacy and views to the South.  Newer wide plank eng. floors, sliders and windows.  Large den can be converted into a 3rd bedroom.  Part of the atrium has been finished into an add'l den.  Adjacent 2 car garage with plenty of storage;  extra parking in driveway. Oceana Community offers many activities incl. 2 pools & spa, pickleball courts, library, card room, art/pottery room, woodshop, dog park.  RV parking (fees) and garden plot when available.  Golf course offers discount on fees. 4 miles from beaches & pier.  Shopping, freeways nearby.
